     \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2023-07-08 16:40:38\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','71124e6c-664f-4ef5-8fbf-e50eda7aaf10','','','2023-07-08 16:40:38','2023-07-08 16:40:38','',0,'http://localhost:8001/?p=1863',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(1864,1,'2023-07-09 09:05:36','2023-07-09 09:05:36','','default','','inherit','open','closed','','default','','','2023-07-09 09:05:36','2023-07-09 09:05:36','',0,'http://localhost:8001/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/default.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1865,1,'2023-07-09 09:05:39','2023-07-09 09:05:39','{\n    \"origamiez::background_image\": {\n        \"value\": \"http://localhost:8001/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/default.jpg\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2023-07-09 09:05:39\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','9cb07e8b-e045-4a4e-9767-d5724aa5234f','','','2023-07-09 09:05:39','2023-07-09 09:05:39','',0,'http://localhost:8001/?p=1865',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(1866,1,'2023-07-11 17:02:08','2023-07-11 17:02:08','<p>Life is a journey that we all embark on, with different paths and destinations. Some of us may travel alone, some may travel with companions, some may travel with a purpose, some may travel without a plan. But no matter how we travel, we all encounter challenges, opportunities, joys and sorrows along the way.</p>\r\n<p>Love is a force that can guide us, inspire us, heal us and transform us. It can be found in many forms and expressions, such as friendship, family, romance, passion, compassion, altruism, gratitude and forgiveness. It can be given and received, shared and cherished, lost and found.</p>\r\n<p>Life and love are intertwined, for they both shape who we are and how we experience the world. They both teach us valuable lessons, such as courage, resilience, empathy, generosity and wisdom. They both challenge us to grow, to change, to adapt, to overcome. They both reward us with happiness, fulfillment, meaning and connection.</p>\r\n<p>But life and love are not always easy or simple. They can also bring pain, disappointment, confusion and regret. They can also test our limits, our faith, our patience and our commitment. They can also demand sacrifices, compromises, risks and choices.</p>\r\n<p>That is why life and love require courage and wisdom. Courage to face the unknown, to embrace the unexpected, to pursue the desired, to overcome the feared. Wisdom to discern the right from the wrong, to balance the needs and wants, to learn from the mistakes, to appreciate the blessings.</p>\r\n<p>Life and love are the greatest gifts that we have. They are also the greatest challenges that we face. They are what make us human and what make us divine. They are what we live for and what we die for.</p>\r\n<p>Life and love are beautiful and precious. Let us cherish them while we can.</p>','Hello world!','','inherit','closed','closed','','1-revision-v1','','','2023-07-11 17:02:08','2023-07-11 17:02:08','',1,'http://localhost:8001/?p=1866',0,'revision','',0),(1867,1,'2023-07-11 17:02:36','2023-07-11 17:02:36','Life is a journey that we all embark on, with different paths and destinations. Some of us may travel alone, some may travel with companions, some may travel with a purpose, some may travel without a plan. But no matter how we travel, we all encounter challenges, opportunities, joys and sorrows along the way.\r\n\r\nLove is a force that can guide us, inspire us, heal us and transform us. It can be found in many forms and expressions, such as friendship, family, romance, passion, compassion, altruism, gratitude and forgiveness. It can be given and received, shared and cherished, lost and found.\r\n\r\nLife and love are intertwined, for they both shape who we are and how we experience the world. They both teach us valuable lessons, such as courage, resilience, empathy, generosity and wisdom. They both challenge us to grow, to change, to adapt, to overcome. They both reward us with happiness, fulfillment, meaning and connection.\r\n\r\nBut life and love are not always easy or simple. They can also bring pain, disappointment, confusion and regret. They can also test our limits, our faith, our patience and our commitment. They can also demand sacrifices, compromises, risks and choices.\r\n\r\nThat is why life and love require courage and wisdom. Courage to face the unknown, to embrace the unexpected, to pursue the desired, to overcome the feared. Wisdom to discern the right from the wrong, to balance the needs and wants, to learn from the mistakes, to appreciate the blessings.\r\n\r\nLife and love are the greatest gifts that we have. They are also the greatest challenges that we face. They are what make us human and what make us divine. They are what we live for and what we die for.\r\n\r\nLife and love are beautiful and precious. Let us cherish them while we can.','Life and Love','','inherit','closed','closed','','1-revision-v1','','','2023-07-11 17:02:36','2023-07-11 17:02:36','',1,'http://localhost:8001/?p=1867',0,'revision','',0);
